Description:
    Generates a video widget that displays a youtube, vimeo or generic video.

Example:
    CMS: obj_class VideoWidget
    CMS: attribute title (html)
    CMS: attribute body (html)
    CMS: attribute source (linklist)
    CMS: attribute width (integer)
    CMS: attribute height (integer)
    CMS: attribute autoplay (boolean)
    CMS: attribute poster (linklist)

    `rails generate cms:widget:video`